divs: Sighting DetailsIt was a warm evening so I decided to spend some time observing the sky in my back yard. I have seen satellites going over my area before so I didn't think too much of this object, but as I watched it coming from the north west heading in a southerly direction it suddenly made A zig zag type of monuver then flashed and disappeared .
